  "texts": [
    "Such a step would facilitate generation of systematic reviews and meta-analysis using one or more of the several AI tools available (Bolaños et al., 2024).",
    "Specialized AI tools could also streamline meta-analyses and support the adoption of speech-based digital biomarkers (Ramanarayanan et al., 2022), a direction ASHA should actively advocate for.",
    "While leveraging the capabilities of AI tools to review and summarize literature, SLPs will need to design tight experiments (Barber, 1976).",
    "We will need to choose data with ethical implications in view, clean the data, choose appropriate algorithms, use walled-off applications to examine the data, evaluate the methods, and query the data by using carefully designed prompts, and watch for hallucinations before analyzing data.",
    "Under no circumstances should AI tool be used to manipulate or misreport data and make false claims (Feng, 2024)."
